## Station Expansions & Walls

**What happens when a corridor wall is destroyed?**

When enemies damage a corridor wall enough to destroy it, all turrets on segments beyond the break lose connection and are disabled. The turret slots on disconnected segments become unavailable until the wall is repaired. Walls automatically repair between levels.

**Can I build on disconnected segments?**

No. If a wall is destroyed and segments are severed from the station core, the turret slots on those segments are disabled and cannot be built upon until the wall is repaired.

