## Armory & Upgrades

**What is the Armory?**

The Armory is a permanent upgrade system where you spend star credits to improve your station across multiple categories. Armory upgrades persist between levels and even through Prestige resets.

**What can I upgrade in the Armory?**

Upgrade categories include turret damage, hull hit points, hull regeneration, shield strength, and more. Each category has up to 50 levels of improvement.

**What are star credits?**

Star credits are the permanent currency earned by completing levels, achieving milestones, and unlocking achievements. They are spent in the Armory on permanent upgrades. Star credits are separate from the in-level currency used to build and upgrade turrets during gameplay.

