## In-App Purchases

**What can I buy?**

Space Station: Defender offers the following in-app purchases:

- **Remove Ads** — A one-time purchase that permanently removes all banner and interstitial ads.
- **Double Credits** — A one-time purchase that permanently doubles all star credit earnings.
- **Starter Pack** — A one-time bundle of star credits to jumpstart your Armory upgrades.
- **Credit Packs** — Various quantities of star credits available for purchase at any time.

**Is the game pay-to-win?**

No. Every level, turret, ability, and expansion can be earned through normal gameplay. In-app purchases allow you to accelerate your progress or remove ads, but they are never required to complete any content.

**How do I restore purchases?**

If you've previously purchased a non-consumable item (Remove Ads, Double Credits, or Starter Pack) and it isn't showing as active, go to the in-game store and tap "Restore Purchases." This will re-validate your purchases with the App Store and restore them to your device.

**I was charged but didn't receive my purchase. What do I do?**

First, try restarting the app and checking your internet connection. If the issue persists, tap "Restore Purchases" in the store. If that doesn't resolve it, please contact Apple Support at [reportaproblem.apple.com](https://reportaproblem.apple.com) for purchase-related billing issues, as all transactions are processed by Apple.

