## Game Center

**What leaderboards are available?**

There are 5 leaderboards:

- **Highest Level Reached** — Your all-time best level (Classic).
- **Total Enemies Defeated** — Lifetime enemy kill count (Classic).
- **Daily Kill Count** — Enemies defeated today (Recurring daily).
- **Longest Win Streak** — Most consecutive levels won (Classic).
- **Total Levels Won** — Lifetime levels completed (Classic).

**How many achievements are there?**

There are 16 achievements worth a total of 405 points, ranging from beginner milestones like "First Blood" (kill 100 enemies) to endgame challenges like "Station Legend" (reach level 100) and "Reborn" (prestige for the first time).

**How do I access leaderboards and achievements?**

From the main menu, tap the "Leaderboards" or "Achievements" button. You can also access them through the Game Center dashboard icon.

**My Game Center progress isn't syncing.**

Ensure you are signed into Game Center in your device Settings under Game Center. The game will attempt to authenticate and sync automatically each time it launches. If you see scores or achievements missing, try closing and reopening the app while connected to the internet.

